I"@	<p>목차
<a href="#간단한-style-등록">1.간단한 style 등록</a>
<a href="#자주-사용하는-속성">2.자주 사용하는 속성</a></p>

<h3 id="간단한-style-등록">간단한 style 등록</h3>
<div class="language-html highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nt">&lt;p</span> <span class="na">style=</span><span class="s">"font-size : 20px; color : red"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span> 글자 <span class="nt">&lt;/p&gt;</span>
</code></pre></div></div>
<ul>
  <li>거의 모든 태그는 style=”” 가능</li>
  <li>스타일이름 : 스타일값;</li>
  <li>세미콜론 <strong>필수</strong></li>
</ul>

<h3 id="자주-사용하는-속성">자주 사용하는 속성</h3>
<div class="language-css highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nc">.box</span> <span class="p">{</span>
	<span class="nl">font-size</span> <span class="p">:</span> <span class="m">20px</span><span class="p">;</span>
	<span class="nl">font-family</span> <span class="p">:</span> <span class="s2">'gulim'</span><span class="p">;</span>
	<span class="nl">color</span> <span class="p">:</span> <span class="no">black</span><span class="p">;</span>
	<span class="nl">letter-spacing</span> <span class="p">:</span> <span class="m">-1px</span><span class="p">;</span>
	<span class="nl">text-align</span> <span class="p">:</span> <span class="nb">center</span><span class="p">;</span>
	<span class="nl">font-weight</span> <span class="p">:</span> <span class="m">600</span><span class="p">;</span>
<span class="p">}</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<h3 id="이미지-정렬-폭-조정">이미지 정렬, 폭 조정</h3>
<div class="language-css highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nc">.box</span> <span class="p">{</span>
    <span class="nl">display</span> <span class="p">:</span> <span class="nb">block</span><span class="p">;</span>
    <span class="nl">margin-left</span> <span class="p">:</span> <span class="nb">auto</span><span class="p">;</span>
    <span class="nl">margin-right</span> <span class="p">:</span> <span class="nb">auto</span><span class="p">;</span>
    <span class="nl">width</span> <span class="p">:</span> <span class="m">150px</span><span class="p">;</span>
<span class="p">}</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

